      <title>Jefferies、Truist 凭借竞争性市政债券交易飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/jefferies-truist-surge-on-competitive-muni-deals-amid-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 和 Truist Financial Corp. 今年在拍卖中赢得了大量市政债券销售，这是花旗集团 (Citigroup Inc.) 等大型银行退出后市场发生震动的最新证据。]]></description>
